{"tid":1830934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港樓價連續十年全球最難負擔　不吃不喝20.8年才能上車","createTime":"2020-01-20T04:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:37:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85574fee79a570f8777ad462481253059617e299","tid":1830934,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"國際公共政策顧問機構Demographia公布「2019年國際房價負擔能力報告」顯示，香港連續第十年登上房價最難負擔城市榜首，房價對家庭入息中位數比率由上年度的歷史高位20.9倍輕微回落至20.8倍，但仍拋離第二位加拿大溫哥華的11.9倍。<br />\n<br />\n據Demographia調查，本港的指數屬嚴重負擔不起（severely unaffordable）級別，回落幅度低於第二及第三位的溫哥華及澳洲悉尼，兩大城市最新的房價對家庭入息中位數比率分別為11.9倍及11倍，2018年分別為12.6倍及11.7倍。<br />\n<br />\n該衡量住宅樓價負擔能力的比率，是以一個城市的房價中位數除以家庭全年入息中位數計算，數值愈大負擔能力愈差。根據香港的最新數字，意味著一個家庭須不吃不喝20.8年才能「上車」做業主。<br />\n<br />\n報告提到，早於殖民地時代（早於70年代），香港的新住宅發展嚴格由政府控制，政府為住宅用地的唯一供應來源，這與實行自由土地使用制度的國家不同，樓價上漲與這種限制性監管環境有關。<br />\n<br />\n然而，近年本港土地供應方式似有所改變，土地供應專責小組建議通過規劃及中長期進行填海發展房屋，冀改善房屋供應及負擔能力。此外，近期私人發展商亦貢獻出部分土地予政府，以紓緩房屋供應短缺情況。"},{"pid":"9efb1ed277dc6cfbe868390fe698ab1374575eb1","tid":1830934,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:23:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1579492378652&amp;issue=20200120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1579492378652%26issue%3D20200120&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=99a52a1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1579492378652%26issue%3D20200120&h=25e0a3ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1579492378652&amp;issue=20200120</a>"},{"pid":"12d1c299e4a2212da43c8696c71172cf238ac525","tid":1830934,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f10d86021ce0bbb8bb54c6aa379c8b026f67fe","tid":1830934,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又贏"},{"pid":"0ecce2221603e44dfaf9f145280d5d37382e84d8","tid":1830934,"uid":21193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66f5ed89c8be72c5bba274ba72f1c631d84c4b8","tid":1830934,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"捐地有撚用咩，咪又係地産商賺哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c1e153cde47770a66a0747e1d9cd25a9142f95","tid":1830934,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港 限制租金"},{"pid":"c89277b84cb2121e9be0438496217c065c15616b","tid":1830934,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:17:35.000Z","msg":"根本已經唔係有冇地就可以解釋到mechanism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家問題係香港嘅樓畀支国搞到變成走支嘅product<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ef9bf0ce7c579840df67b77b4d61369d591f2f","tid":1830934,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:19:32.000Z","msg":"又話遊行有美金收<br />\n<br />\n點解仲係咁難買樓🤔"},{"pid":"400ae30f4f7242fd96f1d937b83a82c303462e39","tid":1830934,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T10:37:08.000Z","msg":"月經"}]}